# Acceptable Use Policy (AUP)
**Scope:** All employees, contractors, and guests using Milot Motors' systems.

## 1. Prohibited Actions
- Using shop laptops for personal social media or illegal downloads.
- Sharing passwords or MFA tokens with other staff members.
- Installing unauthorized software without prior approval from the Risk Officer.

## 2. Reporting
Employees must report any suspicious emails (Phishing) or lost equipment immediately to the Incident Response team.

## 3. Enforcement
Violations of this policy may result in disciplinary action, up to and including termination.

